OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,FIn a speech outside Downing Street,
OL,6,FStarmer confirmed his decision to step
OL,7,Fdown as prime minister and leader of
OL,8,Fthe Labour Party
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer has announced he will
OL,11,Fresign as prime minister less than two
OL,12,Fyears after coming to power.
OL,14,FIn a statement outside 10 Downing
OL,15,FStreet, Sir Keir said his party had
OL,16,Fasked: "Whether I am best placed to
OL,17,Flead us into the next general
OL,18,Felection".
OL,26,@xD@HOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
