CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,FHe said: "I have heard the answer of
OL,6,Fmy parliamentary party to that
OL,7,Fquestion, and I accept that answer
OL,8,Fwith good grace."
OL,10,FDefending his record, he pledged to
OL,11,Fgive his successor "my full and
OL,12,Funequivocal support, knowing that they
OL,13,Fwill inherit a Britain that is far
OL,14,Fstronger and fairer than the one I
OL,15,Finherited two years ago".
OL,17,FHere is everything the prime minister
OL,18,Fsaid in his speech as he set out the
OL,19,Ftimeline for his departure:
OL,26,@mD@JOUpD@QO]sD@TOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"Thank you. Thank you. Walking up this
OL,6,Fstreet two years ago was the proudest
OL,7,Fmoment of my life. A new Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment. The first in 14 years. A
OL,9,Fpage in our country's history turned
OL,10,Fafter years of disappointment and
OL,11,Fdespair.
OL,13,F"The chance to change the lives of
OL,14,Fmillions of people for the better.
OL,15,FThat's what I came into politics for.
OL,16,FThe journey to that point was not easy.
OL,26,@mD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"Six years ago, I inherited a Labour
OL,6,FParty that was politically,
OL,7,Ffinancially and morally bankrupt. I
OL,8,Fwas told, time and time again, that my
OL,9,Fparty was finished.
OL,11,F"That we were consigned to history,
OL,12,Fthat a majority at the general
OL,13,Felection, let alone a landslide
OL,14,Fmajority, was impossible. But we
OL,15,Fproved those people wrong because we
OL,16,Fchanged our party.
OL,18,F"Ripping out the poison of
OL,19,Fantisemitism, restoring trust on the
OL,20,Feconomy, defence, and national
OL,21,Fsecurity.
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"And becoming a party that, once
OL,6,Fagain, stood proudly with, not
OL,7,Fagainst, our national flag. The hard
OL,8,Fwork of change was with a singular
OL,9,Fpurpose. Not power for power's sake
OL,10,Fbut to change Britain for the better.
OL,12,F"To build a fairer country, with
OL,13,Fdignity and respect, where everyone is
OL,14,Fseen, everyone is valued. Wealth and
OL,15,Fopportunity for all, not just the
OL,16,Fprivileged few. And look at what we've
OL,17,Fachieved in just two years.
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"An economy that is stronger, growing
OL,6,Ffaster than our peers. Wages rising
OL,7,Ffaster than inflation in every single
OL,8,Fmonth since we came to power.
OL,9,FInvestment secured, infrastructure
OL,10,Fbeing built. An end to austerity, with
OL,11,Fthe fastest fall in NHS waiting lists
OL,12,Ffor 17 years.
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"The biggest improvement in rights for
OL,6,Fworkers and renters in a generation.
OL,7,FThe biggest uplift in defence spending
OL,8,Fsince the Cold War. Small boat
OL,9,Fcrossings falling, asylum hotels
OL,10,Fclosing, protecting young people from
OL,11,Fsocial media, and half a million
OL,12,Fchildren being lifted out of poverty
OL,13,Fbecause of the choices that I made.
OL,15,F"Our reputation in the world restored,
OL,16,Fwith Britain once again standing up
OL,17,Ffor decency, respect and the rule of
OL,18,Flaw. Securing trade dues, standing
OL,19,Fwith Ukraine, standing up for our
OL,20,Fvalues, and rebuilding our
OL,21,Frelationship with our allies in Europe.
OL,26,@mD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"Change promised by a Labour
OL,6,Fgovernment. Change fought for by a
OL,7,FLabour government, change delivered by
OL,8,Fa Labour government.
OL,10,F"But I know the question being asked
OL,11,Fnow is not who was best placed to
OL,12,Fchange the Labour Party, to take us
OL,13,Finto power, and to begin the vital
OL,14,Fwork of improving lives for millions
OL,15,Fof people. Those questions have been
OL,16,Fanswered.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"The question my party is asking now
OL,6,Fis whether I am best placed to lead us
OL,7,Finto the next general election. I have
OL,8,Fheard the answer of my parliamentary
OL,9,Fparty to that question. And I accept
OL,10,Fthat answer with good grace.
OL,12,F"Every decision I've taken has been
OL,13,Fabout putting the country I love
OL,14,Ffirst. That is why I will resign as
OL,15,Fleader of the Labour Party. I have
OL,16,Fspoken to His Majesty the King this
OL,17,Fmorning to inform him of my decision.
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"I will ask the National Executive
OL,6,FCommittee of the Labour Party to set
OL,7,Fout a timetable with nominations
OL,8,Fopening on the 9th of July and
OL,9,Fcompleted by the summer recess. In the
OL,10,Fcase of a contest, this will ensure a
OL,11,Fnew leader is in place before
OL,12,FParliament returns in September.
OL,14,F"I will remain in post as prime
OL,15,Fminister until the contest is
OL,16,Fcomplete. And I will do everything I
OL,17,Fcan to ensure an orderly handover of
OL,18,Fpower.
OL,26,@mD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"I will also give my successor my full
OL,6,Fand unequivocal support, knowing that
OL,7,Fthey will inherit a Britain that is
OL,8,Ffar stronger and fairer than the one I
OL,9,Finherited two years ago, better
OL,10,Fprepared for the challenges ahead, and
OL,11,Fbetter able to ensure the Labour Party
OL,12,Fsecures a second term in office.
OL,14,F"I want to thank all of those friends
OL,15,Fand colleagues who have been at my
OL,16,Fside for these past six years or so
OL,17,Ffor their incredible commitment,
OL,18,Fservice and support.
OL,26,@mD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782145126
OL,3,CStarmer's resignation speech in full
OL,5,F"I want to thank the brilliant Number
OL,6,F10 staff and our country's
OL,7,Fextraordinary civil service, who
OL,8,Fdedicate their lives to public service.
OL,10,F"And when I leave, the biggest job in
OL,11,Fthe country. I shall spend more time
OL,12,Fon the most important job. Being the
OL,13,Fbest husband I can to my fantastic
OL,14,Fwife, Vic, who has been a rock by my
OL,15,Fside, through good times and bad. And
OL,16,Fbeing the best dad I can to my
OL,17,Fbeautiful children, who are my pride
OL,18,Fand my joy.
OL,20,F"Thank you very much."
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@AOU|D@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
